{"tid":1918543,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Powerbeats 4 無線耳機外洩   擁有 15 小時續航電量","createTime":"2020-03-10T07:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T07:55:10.000Z","uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"081649296538c0f2cd766c64ced719d785334e74","tid":1918543,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"Apple Powerbeats4 上星期現身美國聯邦通訊委員會網站，這款運動型無線耳機預計會在短期內推出，並取代 Powerbeats3。日前有外國傳媒取得了相信是 Powerbeats4 的宣傳影片和相片，還有其規格配置，除了外型設計更符合人體工學，電池續航力亦有所增強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/meZTsQF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmeZTsQF.jpg&h=f4cb9ee8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n全新 Powerbeats4 的機身設計較上一代更纖巧，耳機線材在耳背位置，另配戴使用和運動時都更加舒適。根據德國網站 WinFuture 取得的資料，Powerbeats4 的電池能夠提供長達 15 小時的使用時間。一如所料，Apple 為 Powerbeats4 加入 H1 晶片，新機可以支援 Hey Siri 語音操控，而耳機上的 Beats 商標同時是操控音樂播放和接聽電話的按鈕，跟 AirPods 一樣支援雙點擊和長按等操作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7giUchm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7giUchm.jpg&h=c2b288f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從現階段公開的照片，可以見到 Powerbeats4 將會有黑、白、紅 3 色機身選擇，相信會跟其他 Powerbeats 系列耳機一樣採用 Lightning 接口充電。網站 9to5mac 估計 Apple Powerbeats4 將會隨同 iOS 13.4 於短期內上市。<br />\n<br />\n來源：9to5mac"},{"pid":"01ab6bc791744ffc4de7f7286f1570f31b4b3edc","tid":1918543,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:23:57.000Z","msg":"有條線唔驚跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415c90e11ed4cdafd32f44b2c6000a8b9e8addde","tid":1918543,"uid":43520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01ab6bc791744ffc4de7f7286f1570f31b4b3edc","tid":1918543,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:23:57.000Z","msg":"有條線唔驚跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"科技差不多到頂, 是時候回歸原始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}